---
title: Mediterranean Veggie Pizza with Sundried Tomato Pesto Sauce and Olives
description: Savour the vibrant flavours of this delicious Mediterranean pizza, topped with rich sun-dried tomato pesto, sweet peppers, and briny olives. Paired with a bright green salad with feta, this dish is a satisfying and well-rounded meal.

